### GET TOURNAMENTS
GET http://localhost:3001/tournaments HTTP/1.1

### GET TOURNAMENT BY ID
GET http://localhost:3001/tournaments/7 HTTP/1.1

### CREATE TOURNAMENT
POST http://localhost:3001/tournaments HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "new",
    "player_ids": [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 9]
}

### ADVANCE TOURNAMENT
PUT http://localhost:3001/tournaments/7/advance HTTP/1.1

### FINISH TOURNAMENT
PUT http://localhost:3001/tournaments/7/finish HTTP/1.1

### DELETE TOURNAMENT
DELETE http://localhost:3001/tournaments/6 HTTP/1.1